data.description: MLS# 273276 Introducing a stunning new home to the market! This property is perfect for anyone seeking a modern and updated living space. With numerous fantastic updates and features, it is sure to catch your attention.This home boasts a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom layout, with a spacious main-level living room and a cozy basement family room in the finished basement. One of the standout features is the brand new flooring throughout the entire house, providing a fresh and stylish look.The roof was recently replaced in 2019, ensuring long-term durability and protection for the home. Additionally, the AC and furnace were upgraded in 2020, guaranteeing optimal comfort and energy efficiency. The new fence, installed in 2021, offers privacy and security for the backyard.Parking is a breeze with a 2-car garage and an additional 2-car shop, providing ample space for vehicles and storage. The driveway has a capacity to accommodate 6-8 cars, making it convenient for households with multiple vehicles or guests. When it comes to security, this home has you covered. It comes equipped with a full Ring security system and 4 security cameras that will remain with the property, ensuring peace of mind and added protection. All the appliances in the home will be staying, including a Samsung smart fridge, Samsung smart washer and dryer, as well as a Whirlpool oven, dishwasher, and microwave. These modern and efficient appliances make everyday tasks a breeze. The lot size is approximately 9,990 square feet, providing plenty of outdoor space for various activities and potential landscaping projects. For an added layer of convenience and security, the front door is equipped with a keypad deadbolt, and you will receive keys for all exterior doors. In summary, this home offers a range of updates and features that will enhance your living experience. It is situated in a great location and is sure to impress. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning new home yours! Call your favorite realtor today for a showing and information.
